movies.title: Apollo 11
movies.plot: A look at the Apollo 11 mission to land on the moon led by commander Neil Armstrong and pilot Buzz Aldrin.
movies.awards: Nominated for 1 BAFTA Film Award. Another 52 wins & 35 nominations.
